<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-09-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-02-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="411" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d411">
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                                </head>
                                <p>The Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_845">p.
                                        845</ref>, states that during the morning Roosevelt received
                                    Norman Robertson, the Canadian Under Secretary for External
                                    Affairs. No record of the discussion has been found.</p>
                            </div>
